data.title: Esther Rolle and Bill Macy
data.text: View of actress Esther Rolle and actor Bill Macy in a scene from the television series, "Maude." Label on back: "CBS, Bill Macy, starring as Walter Findlay, is not overjoyed about getting dinner from Esther Rolle, as housekeeper Florida Evans, when Maude's part-time job selling real estate keeps her out a night, on 'Maude,' Tuesday, Oct. 23 (8:00-8:30 PM, EDT) on the CBS Television Network. Photo Division, CBS Television Network press information, 51 West 52 Street, New York, New York 10019."
